{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a long talk, Sharansky and I, about his father and his father's whereabouts during this period.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we believe he was part of the unit that liberated me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to be very careful not to give my current interpretation of what I thought at the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I recall, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we became increasingly more and more aware of the-- of the nightmare quality of this man, his hatred, his venom, his viciousness.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But through some mysterious disconnect, which to this moment, I cannot explain or understand, it seemed implausible to my highly civilized, cultured, democratically inclined, humanitarian family as to what the final outcome could be.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it-- it did not seem plausible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I have a great deal of difficulty giving you a rational or logical explanation because-- because the people I was listening to and I was-- I obviously was just a boy so I didn't participate.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I listened more than I spoke, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were very intelligent people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But obviously blind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not personally.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't recall any personally, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it really came in-- in three segments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first one was the calling up of my uncle and cousins for labor-- compulsory labor service on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of our attention, of course, was devoted to them-- how to get a package to them, can we get mail from them, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was highly personal because this was a very tight knit family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the four young men in the family, my uncle and the three boys, who were-- who were anywhere from-- anywhere from six to 15 years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I wasn't part of this group.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
